Teach Finish Later using Label and Delay
  Use Time Sleep with Seconds be Delay
  Success Label

Teach Fail Later using Message
  Failure Message

Make Task A be Spawn Use Finish Later with "alpha" and 0.01
Make Task B be Spawn Use Finish Later with "beta" and 0.02
Make Tasks be List with Task A and Task B
Make All Values be Need Await Use Async All with Tasks
Expect Item 0 of All Values is "alpha"
Expect Item 1 of All Values is "beta"

Make Slow be Spawn Use Finish Later with "slow" and 0.05
Make Fast be Spawn Use Finish Later with "fast" and 0
Make Race Tasks be List with Slow and Fast
Make Race Result be Need Await Use Async Race with Race Tasks
Expect Race Result is "fast"

Make Failed be Spawn Use Fail Later with "not ready"
Try
  Make Ignored be Need Await Use Async All with List with Failed
  Expect false is true
Catch Error
  Expect Error is "not ready"
